import { combineReducers } from "redux"
import wellsReducer from "./wellsReducer"
import selectWellFromLocalStateReducer from "./selectWellFromLocalStateReducer"
import postPlansToJSONdb from "./postPlansToJSONdb"

export default combineReducers({
  wells: wellsReducer,
  selectedWell: selectWellFromLocalStateReducer,
  plansSuccessfullyPosted: postPlansToDynamoDB
})
